                    div.home__photo-third.foto
                        img(src="../img/photo-3.jpg", alt="Фото-3")
            section.text.container
                .text__info
                    .text__title
                        h3.info__title Everyday practice shows that the implementation of planning targets entails the process of using and implementing a development model.
                        p.info__item Spontaneous, delicate, audacious, our jewels distinguish themselves with their elegance.
                    .text__button
                        a(href="catalog.html" ).button__catalog Перейти в каталог
                        .button__arrow
