            section.jewelry.container
                h2.jewelry__title.title__all ЮВЕЛИРНЫЕ УКРАШЕНИЯ
                .jewelry__content
                    .jewelry__content_item.item__first
                        .jewelry__content_img.content__img 
                            figure.effect-img
                                img(src="../img/jewelry/jewelry-1.jpg", alt="")
                                figcaption.effect-text
                                    a(href="catalog.html").effect-button Перейти в каталог
                            h4.jewelry__content_rings.content__title Кольца
                            p.jewelry__content_price.content__price 5 500 ₽
                    .jewelry__content_item.item__second
                        .jewelry__content_img.content__img
                            figure.effect-img
                                img(src="../img/jewelry/jewelry-2.jpg", alt="")
                                figcaption.effect-text
                                    a(href="catalog.html").effect-button Перейти в каталог
                            h4.jewelry__content_rings.content__title Серьги
                            p.jewelry__content_price.content__price 4 800 ₽
                    .jewelry__content_item.item__third
                        .jewelry__content_img.content__img
                            figure.effect-img
                                img(src="../img/jewelry/jewelry-3.jpg", alt="")
                                figcaption.effect-text
                                    a(href="catalog.html#bracelet").effect-button Перейти в каталог
                            h4.jewelry__content_rings.content__title Браслеты
                            p.jewelry__content_price.content__price-3 6 900 ₽
                    .jewelry__content_item.item__four
                        .jewelry__content_img.content__img
                            figure.effect-img
                                img(src="../img/jewelry/jewelry-4.jpg", alt="")
                                figcaption.effect-text
                                    a(href="catalog.html#chain").effect-button Перейти в каталог
                            h4.jewelry__content_rings.content__title Цепочки
                            p.jewelry__content_price.content__price-4 3 700 ₽
            section.jewelry__photo
                .owl-carousel.owl-theme
                    //-First slide
                    .item
                        .jewelry__photo-content.container
                            .jewelry__photo-info
                                h3.jewelry__photo-title.text-all It should not be forgotten, however, that the current structure of the organization is an interesting experiment.
                                p.jewelry__photo-text Similarly, the implementation of the planned targets allows you to perform important.
                            .jewelry__photo-foto
                                img(src="../img/jewelry__photo/jewelry__photo-1.jpg", alt="").cont-photo.img-responsive

                    //-Second slide
                    .item
                        .jewelry__photo-content.container
                            .jewelry__photo-info
                                h3.jewelry__photo-title When creating the generator, we used the well-known universal speech code. Text is randomly generated in paragraphs from two to ten sentences per paragraph
                                p.jewelry__photo-text That allows you to make the text more attractive and lively for visual and auditory perception.
                            .jewelry__photo-foto
                                img(src="../img/jewelry__photo/jewelry__photo-2.jpg", alt="").cont-photo.img-responsive

                    //-Third slide
                    .item
                        .jewelry__photo-content.container
                            .jewelry__photo-info
                                h3.jewelry__photo-title Unlike lorem ipsum, the text fish in Russian will fill any layout with an incomprehensible meaning and give a unique flavor of Soviet times.
                                p.jewelry__photo-text Which causes some people bewilderment when trying to read the fish text.
                            .jewelry__photo-foto
                                img(src="../img/jewelry__photo/jewelry__photo-3.jpg", alt="").cont-photo.img-responsive
            section.withlove.container
                .withlove__info
                    h2.withlove__title With love MYEL
                    p.withlove__text.text-all Together, we can build a brighter tomorrow. We use ethical stones and the most eco-responsible raw material possible.
            section.gold
                .gold__image_first
                    img(src="../img/gold/ring-1.jpg", alt="Кольца")
                    p.image-first__text #WITHLOVEMYEL
                .gold__image_second
                    img(src="../img/gold/ring-2.jpg", alt="Кольца")
                    h3.image-first__title.text-all Fairmined Gold: choose ethical gold


                    .text__button.image-first__button
                        a(href="catalog.html" ).button__catalog Перейти в каталог
                        .image-first__arrow
